This paper is primarily focused on developing a phishing detection system using machine learning techniques, which falls under the category of computer security (cs.CR). The paper also discusses the use of key terms and their placement on webpages, which could be related to natural language processing (cs.AI) and information retrieval (cs.IR). The target identification component involves image processing techniques to identify the target website, which could be related to computer vision (cs.CV). Finally, the paper discusses the performance of the machine learning model, which could be related to machine learning (cs.LG).
